宫斗兽场举行，门票将于今天（8 月 12 日）太平洋时间上午 10 点（英国夏令时下午 6 点）开始发售，您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/rod-stewart-tickets/artist/736200%20https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Frod-stewart-tickets%2Fartist%2F736200" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。 </p><figure id="attachment_3782308" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782308" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782308" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="罗德·斯图尔特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Rod-Stewart-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Kirsty-Wigglesworth-WPA-Pool_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3782308" class="wp-caption-text">罗德·斯图尔特 – 图片来源：Kirsty Wigglesworth – WPA Pool/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在最近的一次采访中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-admits-im-aware-my-days-are-numbered-3778626">斯图尔特承认他认为自己的“日子已经屈指可数了”。</a>这位音乐家在接受<em>《太阳报》</em>采访时（通过<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/175511/Rod-Stewart-faces-mortality-My-days-are-numbered"><em>音乐新闻</em></a>）回顾了自己临近 80 岁生日时的生活。</p><p> “我知道我的日子屈指可数，但我没有恐惧，”他说。 “我们都必须在某个时候去世，所以我们都在同一个篮子里。在过去的几年里，我将尽我所能地享受自己。我说很少——可能还有 15 个。我可以轻松做到这一点，伙计，简单。”</p><p>这位摇滚音乐家补充道：“我不像 70 年代和 80 年代那样，我不能熬夜、喝醉、发疯，但仍然有这样的声音。 “现在我必须在每次演出之前和之后保护我的声音。” </p><figure id="attachment_3588730" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588730" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588730" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/rod-stewart-back-catalogue-deal.jpg" alt="罗德·斯图尔特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/rod-stewart-back-catalogue-deal.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/rod-stewart-back-catalogue-deal-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/rod-stewart-back-catalogue-deal-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/rod-stewart-back-catalogue-deal-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/rod-stewart-back-catalogue-deal-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/rod-stewart-back-catalogue-deal-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588730" class="wp-caption-text">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart) 于 2024 年 2 月 13 日在佛罗里达州好莱坞塞米诺尔硬石酒店及好莱坞赌场举行的 Hard Rock Live 表演（图片来源：Ivan Apfel/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>今年 2 月还有报道称，这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-sells-back-catalogue-for-near-100million-3588728">以接近 1 亿美元（7,930 万英镑）的价格出售了他的过往唱片</a>。斯图尔特与欧文·阿佐夫的标志性艺术家达成了交易，该艺术家现在拥有他的出版目录、录制的音乐以及斯图尔特的肖像权和肖像权的股份。</p><p>在给<em><a href="https://www.wsj.com/business/media/rod-stewart-sells-song-catalog-as-music-rights-fundraising-surges-c50ceb4f" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《华尔街日报》</a>的一份声明中，</em>斯图尔特谈到这笔交易时表示：“欧文和我是一对老朋友，我相信我们彼此尊重和钦佩。我一生的工作都在他的掌管下。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-postpones-two-concerts-as-he-recovers-from-covid-19-3782790">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart) 从 COVID-19 中恢复后推迟了两场音乐会，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
