e-moments-of-2024-or-freakshow-3778508">在塞纳河沿岸举行了一场史诗般的开幕式</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>表演了法国歌舞歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-mon-truc-en-plumes-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778447">《Mon truc enplumes》</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a>表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-gojira-perform-ah-ca-ira-in-the-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778455">法国大革命歌曲《Ah Ça Ira!》。</a>与歌剧歌手玛丽娜·维奥蒂。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳·迪翁 (Celine Dion)</a>也是四年来首次演出，自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-reveals-stiff-person-syndrome-diagnosis-reschedules-and-cancels-shows-3363354">2022 年透露自己被诊断出患有僵人综合症 (SPS) 以来，她在首场演出中演绎了伊迪丝·琵雅芙 (Edith Piaf) 的《L&#39;Hymne A L&#39;Amour》。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-phoenix-team-up-with-air-vampire-weekends-ezra-koenig-and-kavinsky-at-closing-ceremony-of-paris-olympics-2024-3782740">《Watch Phoenix》与 Air、Vampire Weekend 的 Ezra Koenig 和 Kavinsky 携手亮相 2024 年巴黎奥运会闭幕式的</a>帖子首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ;
